{"tid":1865601,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"64歲米路吉遜 73歲丹尼高化 89歲導演李察當納 再拍《轟天炮》第五集","createTime":"2020-02-06T09:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T15:54:44.000Z","uid":41343,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"182b55602fdcf6b0e2113a309c5e89cd6edc3775","tid":1865601,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:14:22.000Z","msg":"由荷里活兩大影星米路吉遜（Mel Gibson）與丹尼高化（Danny Glover）合演的經典動作片《轟天炮》（Lethal Weapon）不時都被傳出開拍第五集的消息，但一直只聞樓梯響。不過最近美籍華裔監製林暐受訪時就自爆將開拍《轟》第五集！除了導演李察當納之外，兩位「老差骨」主角都會回歸，林暐更透露第五集將會是最後一集。98年推出的第四集除了米路與丹尼之外，亦有李連杰加盟飾演奸角與米路上演肉搏戰。由於相隔二十二年再拍，米路已年屆64歲而丹尼就73歲，唔知仲可唔可以應付片中動作鏡頭？"},{"pid":"d2f836b9e9a25e927d365f2873e412ad6179dc86","tid":1865601,"uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfMqneW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfMqneW.jpg&h=1c4d2a73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ea6c48267e2d29d5ba051539ad664d662d2fd52","tid":1865601,"uid":2507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"全部用替身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c0f0771f8053b1f163772dc99d99a6c8dec575","tid":1865601,"uid":149662,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:30:22.000Z","msg":"搵兩個後生仔然後key佢哋兩個個頭落去<br />\n官人我又要都係咁拍啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff698d2e15bc4758bb851920ac1b7c498c100500","tid":1865601,"uid":286155,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2ea6c48267e2d29d5ba051539ad664d662d2fd52","tid":1865601,"uid":2507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"全部用替身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 